Facebook Buys Israel’s Snaptu For $30-$40 Million - TheMarker

-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 
2011-03-20T09:44:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/facebook-buys-israel-s-snaptu-for-30-40-million-themarker.html
Facebook Inc. has purchased Israeli
start-up Snaptu for between $30-$40 million, and will announce
the acquistion tomorrow, TheMarker financial daily reported
without saying how it got the information.   Snaptu technology enables websites to be turned intp mobile
applications on portable phones, according to the company’s
website. An e-mail to Snaptu requesting comment on the sale did
not elicit an immediate response.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
